item.title: CVE-2023-0600|2024-08-02T05:17:50.061Z -- unknown -- wp%20visitor%20statistics%20%28real%20time%20traffic%29
item.description: The WP Visitor Statistics (Real Time Traffic) WordPress plugin before 6.9 does not escape user input which is concatenated to an SQL query, allowing unauthenticated visitors to conduct SQL Injection attacks.
